{"tid":564779,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男童遭遺棄公園 警方籲提供資料","createTime":"2018-02-18T10:49:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-19T08:00:12.000Z","uid":54733,"like":4,"dislike":81,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"b194e95b18319fcef233f0516d2373845e09a383","tid":564779,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T10:49:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180218/57847317\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180218%2F57847317&d=VuPL272kMKFTdag9%2BRcrvh4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=8483a767\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180218%2F57847317&h=aff18594\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180218/57847317</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180218/large/1518935812_266f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180218%2Flarge%2F1518935812_266f.jpg&h=509b542b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男童年約14至18歲，身高約1.7米(政府新聞處圖片)<br />\n<br />\n農曆新年一向是親友聚首一堂的日子，不過一名10多歲男童卻非常不幸，昨日大年初二被發現遭遺棄在將軍澳一個公園之內。<br />\n<br />\n警方是於昨日晚上約11時20分接獲報案，指一名男童懷疑被遺棄在將軍澳寶康路108號一公園內。男童年約14至18歲，身高約1.7米，蓄短黑髮，被發現時身穿黑色外套、黃色上衣、黑色長褲、黃色運動鞋及戴黑色眼鏡。男童沒有表面傷痕，正在將軍澳醫院留院觀察。<br />\n由於男童身上沒有身份證明文件，警方呼籲男童的親人或有資料提供的市民，盡快與任何一間警署聯絡，或致電3661 0831或3661 0832與將軍澳警區人員聯絡，或電郵至 tkodist-rr@police.gov.hk。"},{"pid":"4ffdb457ed405b11e23f951b38c4830be54ebd3c","tid":564779,"uid":26421,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T10:51:09.000Z","msg":"..."},{"pid":"8f6dfdbc7b9c096b03315c4ff2846e1778839f88","tid":564779,"uid":108467,"like":97,"dislike":1,"score":96,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T10:51:34.000Z","msg":"成個弱智咁"},{"pid":"83eac7577905120e22c238c68ba54a79b8b12404","tid":564779,"uid":23635,"like":134,"dislike":2,"score":132,"citedB